# Backend API Configuration
# ===========================

# (Optional) Override the backend target for the Vite dev proxy.
# Default: http://localhost:8080
# Use this if your Spring Boot backend runs on a different host/port during development.
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8080

# (Optional) Use a completely different API origin instead of the Vite proxy.
# Leave empty to use the proxy (recommended for local dev).
# Set this to a full URL (e.g., https://api.example.com) to bypass the proxy and call a remote API directly.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=

